reviewText: If you like to see tanned fitness models posing in revealing bikinis than you should like this video.  Features Amy Fadhli, Monica Brant, Deidre Pagnanelli, Amy Lynn, Debbee Halo, scifi tv star Vicky Pratt, Stacey Lynn, Angel Teves, and Christine Lydon.  Some of the models have more muscle bulk than others, shows each models working out, posing, etc.  Also has some topless nudity.
